  "detailed_description": "<h1>How To Play!</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1707870/extras/f6f15667d8b0eba7c138bafb32453df4.avif?t=1733068625\" width=630 height=142 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>Getting Started</strong></u></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >On the main menu select Play. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Now select how you want to connect. You can host your own game (you pick the game mode and settings), find a game, or join an existing game (using a room code).</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you're looking to host a game, select your desired game mode and choose your game's visibility. You can set your game as public (anyone can join), private (only people who have your room code can join) or local (no remote connections are allowed). Choose your game settings and select start game!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Once you're connected, head to Rifftrax.games on any internet connected device (your phone, a laptop, ipad, etc) </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >On the website, enter your name and the room code you see on your PC/Mac. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can play single player, two players (with a computer controlled bot), or 3-6 players (bot is optional).</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Once everyone has connected and logged in, have the host select Start Game. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >To play the game you enter text on the website and watch the clips playback on your PC/Mac.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>How to Join a Private Game</u></strong> </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >To join a game you need a copy of the game* and a room code. A room code can be provided by a friend or streamers.  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Once you have their code, select Play on the main menu. Select Join. Enter the room code then select Join Game.  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Wait a moment and you will be connected. If you have a mic connected voice chat will start. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >On any internet connected device (your phone, a laptop, ipad, etc) head to  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >On the website, enter your name and the room code you see on your PC/Mac.  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >To play the game you enter text on the website and watch the clips playback on your PC/Mac. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can adjust voice chat settings by pressing pause and selecting Voice Chat. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > * If you want to join a remote game without purchasing the game, ask the host to share their game screen via Zoom, Discord, or Steam. As long as you can see their screen, you're good to go!</p></li></ul></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1707870/extras/13dfa0ddeaa51c9d482ab180fe5cabd9.poster.avif?t=1733068625\" width=600 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1707870/extras/13dfa0ddeaa51c9d482ab180fe5cabd9.webm?t=1733068625\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1707870/extras/13dfa0ddeaa51c9d482ab180fe5cabd9.mp4?t=1733068625\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>RiffTrax: The Game features the stars of the Emmy-nominated, Peabody Award-winning show “Mystery Science Theater 3000”. Comedians Michael J. Nelson, Kevin Murphy and Bill Corbett have been bringing their comedic running MST3K-type commentary to movies of all kinds for over 15 years - and now’s your chance to riff along with them! Gather your friends and see if you can write the best jokes for some of the worst bits of what can loosely be called \"cinema\". Do you have what it takes to be the next movie riffing genius?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1707870/extras/6bef772a00664263638c3401c06504bc.poster.avif?t=1733068625\" width=614 height=194 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1707870/extras/6bef772a00664263638c3401c06504bc.webm?t=1733068625\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1707870/extras/6bef772a00664263638c3401c06504bc.mp4?t=1733068625\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Over 500 movie clips (and counting) from RiffTrax classics such as “Rollergator”, “Attack Of The Super Monsters”, and “Plan 9 From Outer Space”! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1707870/extras/2b82170cf8b0343452f2c307060b1f5e.poster.avif?t=1733068625\" width=614 height=194 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1707870/extras/2b82170cf8b0343452f2c307060b1f5e.webm?t=1733068625\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1707870/extras/2b82170cf8b0343452f2c307060b1f5e.mp4?t=1733068625\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Featuring two exciting ways to play! Write your own riff and watch your comedy genius come to life via text-to-speech. Or leave it to the pros and choose from thousands of expertly crafted riffs from the RiffTrax team.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1707870/extras/14a67aad1009f57197163d4e56c7607c.poster.avif?t=1733068625\" width=614 height=194 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1707870/extras/14a67aad1009f57197163d4e56c7607c.webm?t=1733068625\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1707870/extras/14a67aad1009f57197163d4e56c7607c.mp4?t=1733068625\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Play head-to-head with up to 6 players using any internet connected device as controller. An additional 12 audience members can also play along.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1707870/extras/d4f2ff9a702d020ad2e58ceca65c0ce2.poster.avif?t=1733068625\" width=614 height=194 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1707870/extras/d4f2ff9a702d020ad2e58ceca65c0ce2.webm?t=1733068625\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1707870/extras/d4f2ff9a702d020ad2e58ceca65c0ce2.mp4?t=1733068625\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Play locally or battle riffers from around the world with online multiplayer matchmaking. Supports cross play and features in-game voice chat.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1707870/extras/bb59f52cbb6e6458229b2471daf3a007.poster.avif?t=1733068625\" width=614 height=194 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1707870/extras/bb59f52cbb6e6458229b2471daf3a007.webm?t=1733068625\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1707870/extras/bb59f52cbb6e6458229b2471daf3a007.mp4?t=1733068625\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Streamers, get your entire chat in on the action with Twitch integration. Let your chat vote, choose clips, or even play along!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1707870/extras/13dfa0ddeaa51c9d482ab180fe5cabd9.poster.avif?t=1733068625\" width=600 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1707870/extras/13dfa0ddeaa51c9d482ab180fe5cabd9.webm?t=1733068625\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1707870/extras/13dfa0ddeaa51c9d482ab180fe5cabd9.mp4?t=1733068625\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>RiffTrax: The Game features the stars of the Emmy-nominated, Peabody Award-winning show “Mystery Science Theater 3000”. Comedians Michael J. Nelson, Kevin Murphy and Bill Corbett have been bringing their comedic running MST3K-type commentary to movies of all kinds for over 15 years - and now’s your chance to riff along with them! Gather your friends and see if you can write the best jokes for some of the worst bits of what can loosely be called \"cinema\". Do you have what it takes to be the next movie riffing genius?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1707870/extras/6bef772a00664263638c3401c06504bc.poster.avif?t=1733068625\" width=614 height=194 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1707870/extras/6bef772a00664263638c3401c06504bc.webm?t=1733068625\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1707870/extras/6bef772a00664263638c3401c06504bc.mp4?t=1733068625\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Over 500 movie clips (and counting) from RiffTrax classics such as “Rollergator”, “Attack Of The Super Monsters”, and “Plan 9 From Outer Space”! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1707870/extras/2b82170cf8b0343452f2c307060b1f5e.poster.avif?t=1733068625\" width=614 height=194 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1707870/extras/2b82170cf8b0343452f2c307060b1f5e.webm?t=1733068625\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1707870/extras/2b82170cf8b0343452f2c307060b1f5e.mp4?t=1733068625\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Featuring two exciting ways to play! Write your own riff and watch your comedy genius come to life via text-to-speech. Or leave it to the pros and choose from thousands of expertly crafted riffs from the RiffTrax team.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1707870/extras/14a67aad1009f57197163d4e56c7607c.poster.avif?t=1733068625\" width=614 height=194 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1707870/extras/14a67aad1009f57197163d4e56c7607c.webm?t=1733068625\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1707870/extras/14a67aad1009f57197163d4e56c7607c.mp4?t=1733068625\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Play head-to-head with up to 6 players using any internet connected device as controller. An additional 12 audience members can also play along.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1707870/extras/d4f2ff9a702d020ad2e58cec